:I034 :hasSymptoms "Sore throat, extreme tiredness, chest pain, low-grade fever, mild chills, cough, sneezing, headache" .
:I004 :hasSymptoms "facial pain, a stuffy or runny nose, and sometimes a fever" .
:I035 :hasSymptoms "needing to pee often, pain while peeing and pain in your side or lower back". 

